source.name: List of Local Education Agencies (School Districts)
source.description: The Common Core of Data survey provides a listing of all schools districts providing free public elementary and secondary education, along with basic descriptive statistical information on each school district listed. Formally known as the Common Core of Data Local Education Agency (School District) Universe Survey Data.
